title: Cute Critter Purses to Crochet
description: Crochet doesn t get cuter than this! Six adorable animals by Cindy Harris make themselves useful as children's purse pets. Bright button eyes and lots of individual detail give the "critters" their appealing personalities. A flap closure keeps necessities safely inside the handbag. Your little sweetheart will be delighted to take her new animal friend with her everywhere she goes. Basic purse to crochet (11" long by 6" tall) and finishing instructions for 6 purse pets: puppy, kitten, bunny, bear, piggy, and cow.
